snippet.title: Marooners Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the game: http://store.steampowered.com/app/423810/

Play a mix of fun party games as you switch back and forth between them. Can you handle the chaos? Join your friends both on the couch and online while sadisticly laughing at their misfortune. Run, jump and slap your way to victory!
